      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/about/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;about&#34;&gt;&#xA;  About&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#about&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Hi there! ☺️&lt;br&gt;&#xA;My name is Dylan.&lt;br&gt;&#xA;I am a student studying Infomation Technology at Wellington Institute of Technology in New Zealand. 🎉&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;what-i-do&#34;&gt;&#xA;  What I do&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#what-i-do&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;I am currently studying Information Security, Discreet Mathematics, Interaction Design, and Programming.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;skills-&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Skills 😎&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#skills-&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Languages: JavaScript, CSS, Java, C, C# Bash, Python.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Software: VScode, NeoVim, BlueJ, Git/Github, Obsidian.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Operating systems: Arch linux, Kali linux, Proxmox and anything Debian/Fedora based.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;main-fields-of-interest&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Main Fields of Interest&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#main-fields-of-interest&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;I really enjoy setting up Servers and Network Equipment as well as Building PCs and servers. 🖥️&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Another interest of mine is Home labbing where I have a home server running Proxmox LXCs which host:&#xA;Jellyfin, Immich, Vaultwarden, Beszel, SearXNG, and a VPN all running under Tailscale.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;I also enjoy hacking (ethically of course) and doing CTF challenges (notably NZCSC 2023 where my team came 20th in the country).&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;outside-of-it-and-university&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Outside of IT and University&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#outside-of-it-and-university&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;When I am not working on any University or Personal projects I like to:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
