      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;my-projects&#34;&gt;&#xA;  My Projects&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#my-projects&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Welcome to my projects page! Below you&amp;rsquo;ll find a list of my recent projects along with descriptions and links to their GitHub repositories.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;projects&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Projects&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#projects&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;university-projects&#34;&gt;&#xA;  University Projects&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#university-projects&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Description:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;Unfortunately, because all my courses were introductory, I did not create any projects this year. Instead, what the University did is provide us with half-completed code which we are expected to complete for our assignments. These are copyrighted, so I cannot publish them here.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Date:&lt;/strong&gt; 2025&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;java-snake-game&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Java snake game&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#java-snake-game&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Description:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;Made this game as my year 13 project in my Computer Science High School class. This was made to be easy to beat so the snake extends infinitly.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;GitHub Link:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/Dizzle0/CSC335-Project&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;CSC335-Project&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Date:&lt;/strong&gt; 2024&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;prisoners-dilemma&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Prisoners Dilemma&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#prisoners-dilemma&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Description:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;Text based Prisoners Dilemma game made in java. This was my year 12 Computer Science project.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;GitHub Link:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/Dizzle0/prisoners-dilemma&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;prisoners-dilemma&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Date:&lt;/strong&gt; 2023&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;unity-game&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Unity Game&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#unity-game&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Description:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;Unity Game I made at a 3 day Game Dev course.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;GitHub Link:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/Dizzle0/Unity-Game&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Unity-Game&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Date:&lt;/strong&gt; 2022&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;arduino-robot&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Arduino Robot&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#arduino-robot&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Description:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;Arduino Robot which I made in year 11 Robotics Club in High School.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;GitHub Link:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/Dizzle0/Arduino-Robot&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Arduino-Robot&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Date:&lt;/strong&gt; 2022&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;car-game&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Car Game&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#car-game&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Description:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;Basic car game made in HTML and javascript that I made in year 11 Computer Science.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Game Link:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://cargame.pages.dev&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Car Game&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;GitHub Link:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/Dizzle0/Car-Game&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Car-Game&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Date:&lt;/strong&gt; 2022&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;contact&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Contact&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;heading-link&#34; href=&#34;#contact&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;i class=&#34;fa-solid fa-link&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34; title=&#34;Link to heading&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&#xA;    &lt;span class=&#34;sr-only&#34;&gt;Link to heading&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Feel free to &lt;a href=&#34;https://dizzled.dev/contact&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;reach out&lt;/a&gt; for collaboration or feedback.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
